cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image-based representations and generative models for indoor scene synthesis. It could also belong to Graphics (cs.GR) as it involves the creation of synthetic scenes. The use of neural network modules suggests it could be in the Machine Learning (cs.LG) or Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the iterative insertion of objects and the use of deep convolutional models suggest it could also be in the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-category.
